headline: 1 Magnificent S&P 500 High-Yield Dividend Stock Down 25% to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Simply picking the highest yielding stocks off a list, like the companies in the S&P 500 index, won't do.  You need to aim higher, looking for high-yield dividend stocks that you can count on and, better yet, trying to buy them when they are on sale.  Realty Income (NYSE: O) is one of the largest internationally diversified real estate investment trusts (REITs) you can buy.
